    "content": "✅ Approved the contribution.\nComment: Elle respecte toutes les règles, j'ai fait cette solution :\n\nsentence = input()\n\ns = sentence.split()\n\nres = \"\"\n\nfor elt in s:\n    if elt in [\"my\", \"MY\", \"My\", \"mY\"]:\n        res = \"Our \" + s[s.index(elt)+1]\n        break\n\nwhile res[-1] in [\".\", \"!\", \"?\", \",\"]:\n    res = res[:-1]\n\nres += \".\"\n\nprint(res)",
    "codingamerHandle": "602b05c151c3e660ffc9c2a4700225523212517",
    "avatar": 159105646737867,
    "elapsedTime": 183346000
